# thread-project-template/.claudeignore
# NOTE: As of May 2026, Claude Code does NOT natively support .claudeignore.
# This template is shipped for two reasons:
#   1. Future-proofing: if/when Claude Code adds native support (issue #29455
#      was closed as duplicate; the feature is actively requested), this file
#      will be picked up.
#   2. Documentation: it documents which paths a learner should NOT expose
#      to Claude Code's context.
# For HARD enforcement today, see .claude/settings.json `permissions.deny`.

node_modules/
.next/
dist/
build/
coverage/
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
.DS_Store
*.log
.planning/
